ane transporter activity\")\nsrc/ontology/go-edit-filtered-xrefs.ofn:183949:AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasNarrowSynonym> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0015416> \"alkylphosphonate transmembrane-transporting ATPase activity\")\nsrc/ontology/go-edit-filtered-xrefs.ofn:184028:AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> \"GOC:pz\") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> \"RHEA:17873\") <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0015420> \"Enables the transfer of a solute or solutes from one side of a membrane to the other according to the reaction: vitamin B12(out) + ATP + H2O = ADP + an vitamin B12(in) + H+ + phosphate. Vitamin B12 is alkylcob(III)alamin.\")\nsrc/ontology/go-edit-filtered-xrefs.ofn:187259:AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasNarrowSynonym> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0015716> \"alkylphosphonate transport\")\nsrc/ontology/go-edit-filtered-xrefs.ofn:198346:# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0016765> (transferase activity, transferring alkyl or aryl (other than methyl) groups)\nsrc/ontology/go-edit-filtered-xrefs.ofn:198348:AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> \"EC:2.5.1.-\") <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0016765> \"Catalysis of the transfer of an alkyl or aryl (but not methyl) group from one compound (donor) to another (acceptor).\")\nsrc/ontology/go-edit-filtered-xrefs.ofn:198352:AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0016765> \"transferase activity, transferring alkyl or aryl groups, other than methyl groups\")\nsrc/ontology/go-edit-filtered-xrefs.ofn:198357:AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0016765> \"transferase activity, transferring alkyl or aryl (other than methyl) groups\")\nsrc/ontology/go-edit-filtered-xrefs.ofn:198753:# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0016802> (trialkylsulfonium hydrolase activity)\nsrc/ontology/go-edit-filtered-xrefs.ofn:198759:AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0016802> \"trialkylsulphonium hydrolase activity\")\nsrc/ontology/go-edit-filtered-xrefs.ofn:198762:AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0016802> \"trialkylsulfonium hydrolase activity\")\nsrc/ontology/go-edit-filtered-xrefs.ofn:211194:# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0018682> (obsolete atrazine N-dealkylase activity)\nsrc/ontology/go-edit-filtered-xrefs.ofn:211202:AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0018682> \"obsolete atrazine N-dealkylase activity\")\nsrc/ontology/go-edit-filtered-xrefs.ofn:211909:# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0018741> (linear primary-alkylsulfatase activity)\nsrc/ontology/go-edit-filtered-xrefs.ofn:211911:AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> \"RHEA:67908\") <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0018741> \"Catalysis of the reaction: a primary linear alkyl sulfate ester + H2O = a primary alcohol + H+ + sulfate.\")\nsrc/ontology/go-edit-filtered-xrefs.ofn:211914:AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasBroadSynonym> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0018741> \"alkyl sulfatase activity\")\nsrc/ontology/go-edit-filtered-xrefs.ofn:211920:AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0018741> \"linear primary-alkylsulfatase activity\")\nsrc/ontology/go-edit-filtered-xrefs.ofn:212359:AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> \"PMID:10464214\") <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0018777> \"OBSOLETE. Catalysis 